            {
                "id": 1670787,
                "public_url": "hackathons/inout-hacks-2026-jss-academy-of-technical-education-jssate-noida-1670787",
                "title": "InOut Hacks 2026",
                "organization_id": 128941,
                "type": "hackathons",
                "subtype": "online_coding_challenge",
                "regn_open": 1,
                "updated_at": "2026-04-05T17:26:26+05:30",
                "region": "offline",
                "visibility": "public",
                "details": "<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"56\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"56\">Step into a realm where innovation meets execution.:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"58\" data-end=\"481\">\n<li data-section-id=\"8sx9e2\" data-start=\"58\" data-end=\"322\">INOUT Hackathon 2026 is a 36-hour, inter-college hackathon designed to bring together developers, designers, and problem-solvers to build impactful, real-world solutions &mdash; inspired by the spirit of creation and excellence often associated with Norse Mythology.</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1n5zx1f\" data-start=\"324\" data-end=\"481\">Whether you specialize in coding, design, or ideation, this platform offers you the opportunity to collaborate, innovate, and create meaningful projects.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"507\"><strong data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"507\">Hackathon Structure:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"1006\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1l00nge\" data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"539\">Phase I &ndash; Online Screening</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"16354dy\" data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"563\">Teams will submit:</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1i0n9t6\" data-start=\"564\" data-end=\"588\">A presentation (PPT)</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"12vgi5u\" data-start=\"589\" data-end=\"645\">A short video walkthrough of their proposed solution</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"f2tddx\" data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"718\">Based on evaluation, selected teams will advance to the next phase.</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"ab5v2m\" data-start=\"720\" data-end=\"765\">Phase II &ndash; Offline Finale (JSS Institute)</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1hteuit\" data-start=\"767\" data-end=\"946\">Shortlisted teams will participate in a 36-hour on-site hackathon &mdash; a focused environment where ideas are forged into working solutions with guidance from experienced mentors.</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1rb2i7k\" data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"1006\">Final projects will be presented to a panel of judges.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1027\"><strong data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1027\">What to Expect:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1029\" data-end=\"1320\">\n<li data-section-id=\"x5bkgk\" data-start=\"1029\" data-end=\"1078\">Collaborative environment with talented peers</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1gy36q0\" data-start=\"1079\" data-end=\"1132\">Mentorship from industry professionals and alumni</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"968gjy\" data-start=\"1133\" data-end=\"1168\">Food and accommodation provided</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"l6varz\" data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1253\">Rewards including cash prizes, trophies, certificates, and exclusive merchandise</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1kczj2g\" data-start=\"1254\" data-end=\"1320\">Participation certificates &amp; goodies for all shortlisted teams</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1322\" data-end=\"1334\"><strong data-start=\"1322\" data-end=\"1334\">Domains:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1484\">\n<li data-section-id=\"13w41ic\" data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1401\">Participants can build solutions across key technology areas:</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"j9hbe9\" data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1420\">Cybersecurity</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"55m49\" data-start=\"1421\" data-end=\"1440\">AI &amp; Automation</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"154u2wc\" data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1455\">Blockchain</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"e7eax2\" data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1484\">Internet of Things (IoT)</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1507\"><strong data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1507\">Why Participate?:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1509\" data-end=\"1740\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1mtb0ah\" data-start=\"1509\" data-end=\"1571\">Build and ship a project within a focused 36-hour timeline</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"102bse8\" data-start=\"1572\" data-end=\"1628\">Gain hands-on experience solving real-world problems</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"1opj1hm\" data-start=\"1629\" data-end=\"1690\">Network with like-minded individuals and industry mentors</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"q2wal9\" data-start=\"1691\" data-end=\"1740\">Strengthen your portfolio with practical work</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1742\" data-end=\"1768\"><strong data-start=\"1742\" data-end=\"1768\">Registration Deadline:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1787\">\n<li data-section-id=\"10lz822\" data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1787\">20 April 2026</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1789\" data-end=\"1806\"><strong data-start=\"1789\" data-end=\"1806\">Closing Note:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1808\" data-end=\"1850\">\n<li data-section-id=\"14nltan\" data-start=\"1808\" data-end=\"1850\">Build. Innovate. Stand among the best.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1852\" data-end=\"1875\"><strong data-start=\"1852\" data-end=\"1875\">Join the Community:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1877\" data-end=\"2179\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\n<li data-section-id=\"1803x5x\" data-start=\"1877\" data-end=\"2023\">Stay updated with the latest announcements, connect with fellow participants, find teammates, and get your doubts resolved &mdash; all in one place.</li>\n<li data-section-id=\"44209y\" data-start=\"2025\" data-end=\"2105\">Join our WhatsApp Community <a class=\"decorated-link\" href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/GmY2rOhEwUD1JxGIll4tYu\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"2055\" data-end=\"2103\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/GmY2rOhEwUD1JxGIll4tYu</a></li>\n<li data-section-id=\"q1rhm1\" data-start=\"2107\" data-end=\"2179\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Be a part of the conversation and stay ahead throughout the hackathon!</li>\n</ul>",
